    <title>大数据常见 SQL 面试题</title>
    <url>/2024/07/30/bigdata-sql/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="一、用户登录问题"><a href="#一、用户登录问题" class="headerlink" title="一、用户登录问题"></a>一、用户登录问题</h1><h2 id="1）最大连续活跃天数"><a href="#1）最大连续活跃天数" class="headerlink" title="1）最大连续活跃天数"></a>1）最大连续活跃天数</h2><p>有一张用户在线记录表，表结构如下，使用任意引擎SQL，得出每个user_id，最大的连续活跃天数max_act_day。</p>
<p>最大连续活跃天数：每个连续日期天范围内，每日都有在线记录，其中最大的连续日期天个数</p>
<p><img src="https://jinke.love/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/20240326115836116-image.png" alt="user_id用户id，online_time用户在线时间"></p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 先处理数据表粒度到用户/日期并去重</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> user_id, date_format(online_time, <span class="string">&#x27;yyyy-MM-dd&#x27;</span>) online_time</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> source_table</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">group</span> <span class="keyword">by</span> user_id, date_format(online_time, <span class="string">&#x27;yyyy-MM-dd&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 按照用户分组处理日期，当前日期➗分组内日期排序，如果是连续登录则login_day会保持一致</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> user_id, date_sub(online_time, <span class="built_in">ROW_NUMBER</span>() <span class="keyword">OVER</span>(<span class="keyword">PARTITION</span> <span class="keyword">BY</span> user_id <span class="keyword">ORDER</span> <span class="keyword">BY</span> online_time <span class="keyword">ASC</span>)) login_day</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> source_table_a;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 在上面SQL的基础上继续处理，求出连续登录天数</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> user_id, login_day, <span class="built_in">count</span>(<span class="number">1</span>) login_count</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> source_table_b</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">group</span> <span class="keyword">by</span> user_id, login_day;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 在上面SQL的基础上求最值即可</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> user_id, <span class="built_in">max</span>(login_count) max_active_day</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> source_table_c</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">group</span> <span class="keyword">by</span> user_id;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 合并上述SQL</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> user_id, <span class="built_in">max</span>(login_count) max_active_day</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> (</span><br><span class="line">  	<span class="comment">-- 求出连续登录天数</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">select</span> user_id, login_day, <span class="built_in">count</span>(<span class="number">1</span>) login_count</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">from</span> (</span><br><span class="line">      		<span class="comment">-- 按照用户分组处理日期，当前日期➗分组内日期排序，如果是连续登录则login_day会保持一致</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">select</span> user_id, </span><br><span class="line">      		date_sub(online_time, <span class="built_in">ROW_NUMBER</span>() <span class="keyword">OVER</span>(<span class="keyword">PARTITION</span> <span class="keyword">BY</span> user_id <span class="keyword">ORDER</span> <span class="keyword">BY</span> online_time <span class="keyword">ASC</span>)) login_day</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">from</span> (</span><br><span class="line">      	<span class="comment">-- 先处理数据表粒度到用户/日期并去重</span></span><br><span class="line">      	<span class="keyword">select</span> user_id, date_format(online_time, <span class="string">&#x27;yyyy-MM-dd&#x27;</span>) online_time</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">from</span> source_table</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">group</span> <span class="keyword">by</span> user_id, date_format(online_time, <span class="string">&#x27;yyyy-MM-dd&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">      )source_table_a</span><br><span class="line">    )source_table_b</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">group</span> <span class="keyword">by</span> user_id, login_day</span><br><span class="line">) source_table_c</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">group</span> <span class="keyword">by</span> user_id;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">-- 使用临时数据替换 source_table</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">select</span> user_id, <span class="built_in">max</span>(login_count) max_active_day</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> (</span><br><span class="line">  	<span class="comment">-- 求出连续登录天数</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">select</span> user_id, login_day, <span class="built_in">count</span>(<span class="number">1</span>) login_count</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">from</span> (</span><br><span class="line">      		<span class="comment">-- 按照用户分组处理日期，当前日期➗分组内日期排序，如果是连续登录则login_day会保持一致</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="keyword">select</span> user_id, </span><br><span class="line">      		date_sub(online_time, <span class="built_in">ROW_NUMBER</span>() <span class="keyword">OVER</span>(<span class="keyword">PARTITION</span> <span class="keyword">BY</span> user_id <span class="keyword">ORDER</span> <span class="keyword">BY</span> online_time <span class="keyword">ASC</span>)) login_day</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">from</span> (</span><br><span class="line">      	<span class="comment">-- 先处理数据表粒度到用户/日期并去重</span></span><br><span class="line">      	<span class="keyword">select</span> user_id, date_format(online_time, <span class="string">&#x27;yyyy-MM-dd&#x27;</span>) online_time</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">from</span> (<span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="number">1</span> user_id, ‘<span class="number">2024</span><span class="number">-01</span><span class="number">-01</span> <span class="number">01</span>:<span class="number">01</span>:<span class="number">01</span>’ online_time</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">UNION</span> <span class="keyword">all</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="number">1</span> user_id, ‘<span class="number">2024</span><span class="number">-01</span><span class="number">-02</span> <span class="number">01</span>:<span class="number">01</span>:<span class="number">01</span>’ online_time</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">UNION</span> <span class="keyword">all</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="number">1</span> user_id, ‘<span class="number">2024</span><span class="number">-01</span><span class="number">-03</span> <span class="number">01</span>:<span class="number">01</span>:<span class="number">01</span>’ online_time</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">UNION</span> <span class="keyword">all</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="number">1</span> user_id, ‘<span class="number">2024</span><span class="number">-01</span><span class="number">-05</span> <span class="number">01</span>:<span class="number">01</span>:<span class="number">01</span>’ online_time</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">UNION</span> <span class="keyword">all</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="number">2</span> user_id, ‘<span class="number">2024</span><span class="number">-01</span><span class="number">-02</span> <span class="number">01</span>:<span class="number">01</span>:<span class="number">01</span>’ online_time</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">UNION</span> <span class="keyword">all</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="number">2</span> user_id, ‘<span class="number">2024</span><span class="number">-01</span><span class="number">-05</span> <span class="number">01</span>:<span class="number">01</span>:<span class="number">01</span>’ online_time</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">UNION</span> <span class="keyword">all</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="number">2</span> user_id, ‘<span class="number">2024</span><span class="number">-01</span><span class="number">-06</span> <span class="number">01</span>:<span class="number">01</span>:<span class="number">01</span>’ online_time</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">UNION</span> <span class="keyword">all</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="number">2</span> user_id, ‘<span class="number">2024</span><span class="number">-01</span><span class="number">-07</span> <span class="number">01</span>:<span class="number">01</span>:<span class="number">01</span>’ online_time</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">UNION</span> <span class="keyword">all</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="number">3</span> user_id, ‘<span class="number">2024</span><span class="number">-01</span><span class="number">-01</span> <span class="number">01</span>:<span class="number">01</span>:<span class="number">01</span>’ online_time</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">UNION</span> <span class="keyword">all</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="number">3</span> user_id, ‘<span class="number">2024</span><span class="number">-01</span><span class="number">-02</span> <span class="number">01</span>:<span class="number">01</span>:<span class="number">01</span>’ online_time</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">UNION</span> <span class="keyword">all</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="number">3</span> user_id, ‘<span class="number">2024</span><span class="number">-01</span><span class="number">-03</span> <span class="number">01</span>:<span class="number">01</span>:<span class="number">01</span>’ online_time</span><br><span class="line">                ) source_table</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">group</span> <span class="keyword">by</span> user_id, date_format(online_time, <span class="string">&#x27;yyyy-MM-dd&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">      )source_table_a</span><br><span class="line">    )source_table_b</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">group</span> <span class="keyword">by</span> user_id, login_day</span><br><span class="line">) source_table_c</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">group</span> <span class="keyword">by</span> user_id;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>











]]></content>
