  <entry>
    <title>一些常用的 Hive 时间日期函数</title>
    <url>/2024/07/30/hive-function/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p><strong>参考文档：</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><p><a href="https://nightlies.apache.org/flink/flink-docs-release-1.19/zh/docs/dev/table/functions/systemfunctions/#%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0">Flink时间日期函数</a></p>
</li>
<li><p><a href="https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/Hive/Hive+UDFs#HiveUDFs-DateFunctions">HiveUDFs-DateFunctions</a></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="日期和时间的提取"><a href="#日期和时间的提取" class="headerlink" title="日期和时间的提取"></a>日期和时间的提取</h3><ul>
<li><p><code>CURRENT_DATE</code>: 返回当前日期。</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="built_in">CURRENT_DATE</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2024</span><span class="number">-07</span><span class="number">-30</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p><code>CURRENT_TIMESTAMP</code>: 返回当前时间戳。</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="built_in">CURRENT_TIMESTAMP</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2024</span><span class="number">-07</span><span class="number">-30</span> <span class="number">22</span>:<span class="number">10</span>:<span class="number">10.816</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
<span id="more"></span>

<ul>
<li><p><code>UNIX_TIMESTAMP([string date])</code>: 将日期字符串转换为Unix时间戳（秒数）。</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> UNIX_TIMESTAMP(<span class="string">&#x27;2024-07-29 12:34:56&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">1722227696</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p><code>FROM_UNIXTIME(int)</code>: 将Unix时间戳转换为日期字符串。</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> FROM_UNIXTIME(<span class="number">1627568496</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2021</span><span class="number">-07</span><span class="number">-29</span> <span class="number">22</span>:<span class="number">21</span>:<span class="number">36</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p><code>TO_DATE(string timestamp)</code>: 将时间戳字符串转换为日期。</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> TO_DATE(<span class="string">&#x27;2024-07-29 12:34:56&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">2024</span><span class="number">-07</span><span class="number">-29</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="日期的格式化和转换"><a href="#日期的格式化和转换" class="headerlink" title="日期的格式化和转换"></a>日期的格式化和转换</h3><ul>
<li><p><code>DATE_FORMAT(date/timestamp/string ts, string fmt)</code>: 将日期、时间戳或日期字符串格式化为指定的字符串格式。</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> DATE_FORMAT(<span class="string">&#x27;2024-07-29&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;yyyy-MM-dd&#x27;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p><code>CAST(expression AS date)</code>: 将表达式转换为日期类型。</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="built_in">CAST</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;2024-07-29 12:34:56&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">AS</span> <span class="type">date</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="built_in">CAST</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;2024-07-29 12:34:56&#x27;</span> <span class="keyword">AS</span> <span class="type">TIMESTAMP</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p><code>TO_DATE(string timestamp)</code>: 将时间戳字符串转换为日期。</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> TO_DATE(<span class="string">&#x27;2024-07-29 12:34:56&#x27;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p><code>Flink:</code> <code>TO_TIMESTAMP(string date)</code>将日期字符串转换为时间戳。</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> TO_TIMESTAMP(<span class="string">&#x27;2024-07-29 12:34:56&#x27;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="日期计算"><a href="#日期计算" class="headerlink" title="日期计算"></a>日期计算</h3><ul>
<li><p><code>DATE_ADD(date/timestamp startdate, int days)</code>: 返回指定日期加上若干天后的日期。</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> DATE_ADD(<span class="string">&#x27;2024-07-29&#x27;</span>, <span class="number">5</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p><code>DATE_SUB(date/timestamp startdate, int days)</code>: 返回指定日期减去若干天后的日期。</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> DATE_SUB(<span class="string">&#x27;2024-07-29&#x27;</span>, <span class="number">5</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p><code>DATEDIFF(string enddate, string startdate)</code>: 返回两个日期之间的天数差。</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> DATEDIFF(<span class="string">&#x27;2024-07-29&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;2024-07-25&#x27;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="日期部分提取"><a href="#日期部分提取" class="headerlink" title="日期部分提取"></a>日期部分提取</h3><ul>
<li><p><code>YEAR(date/timestamp/string)</code>: 返回日期的年份部分。</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="keyword">YEAR</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;2024-07-29&#x27;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p><code>MONTH(date/timestamp/string)</code>: 返回日期的月份部分。</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="keyword">MONTH</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;2024-07-29&#x27;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p><code>DAY(date/timestamp/string)</code>: 返回日期的天数部分。</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="keyword">DAY</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;2024-07-29&#x27;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p><code>HOUR(date/timestamp/string)</code>: 返回时间的小时部分。</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="keyword">HOUR</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;2024-07-29 12:34:56&#x27;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p><code>MINUTE(date/timestamp/string)</code>: 返回时间的分钟部分。</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="keyword">MINUTE</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;2024-07-29 12:34:56&#x27;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p><code>SECOND(date/timestamp/string)</code>: 返回时间的秒数部分。</p>
<figure class="highlight sql"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">SELECT</span> <span class="keyword">SECOND</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;2024-07-29 12:34:56&#x27;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>基础知识整理</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>SQL</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
